+
+List, get, set, and initialize config properties. Secrets are \
+handled with masked input and displayed as set/unset.
+
+Examples:
+  zeroclaw props list                         # list all properties
+  zeroclaw props list --filter gateway        # filter by prefix
+  zeroclaw props list --secrets               # show secret fields
+  zeroclaw props get gateway.port             # get a value
+  zeroclaw props set gateway.port 9090        # set a value
+  zeroclaw props set api_key                  # prompt for secret
+  zeroclaw props init                         # init defaults
+  zeroclaw props init channels.telegram       # init one section
+  zeroclaw props complete gate                # tab-completion")]
